synthesis_method: A composite solid electrolyte was generated by substituting Li6.4La3Zr1.4Nb0.6O12 for Li6.4La3Zr1.4Nb0.6O12 in Example 3, with Li6.4La3Zr1.4Nb0.6O12 synthesized using LiOH(H2O), La(OH)3, ZrO2, and Nb2O5, within a temperature range of 500 to 1300°C, and confirmed to have an average particle diameter of around 10 μm via SEM analysis.
